oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Waylon Jennings Live in Concert - 1975-08-19
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is from Waylon Jennings' (musician) live performance at the Exit. The performance was on August 19, 1975. The tape was created by the WHN radio network.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Waylon Jennings
